description: SpareBank 1 Østlandet provides various financial products and services to individuals, businesses, public entities, teams, and associations. It operates through the Retail, Corporate, and Organisation Market and Capital Market segments. The Retail segment offers financial services comprising savings, financing, payment processing, insurance, loss prevention, capital management, and investments. The Corporate segment provides hedging for interest and foreign exchange transactions, placement of surplus liquidity, insurance for individuals, pension solutions, as well as coverage for buildings and movable property. The Organisation Market and Capital Market segment delivers risk-adjusted advisory solutions to private customers and businesses, and it also engages in foreign currency services. SpareBank 1 Østlandet was founded in 1845 and is headquartered in Hamar, Norway.
